00:04:00.170 --> 00:04:01.380
Really?

00:04:03.040 --> 00:04:06.380
From what I remember,
you didn't look like you were lying.

00:04:07.080 --> 00:04:08.500
If I'm wrong, that's fine.

00:04:08.670 --> 00:04:13.420
But I figure even vampires can
have problems, you know?

00:04:16.210 --> 00:04:18.710
Hey, wanna go sing karaoke?

00:04:20.580 --> 00:04:22.670
So where's Nazuna?
She okay with this?

00:04:22.670 --> 00:04:25.000
She was exasperated but said to do whatever.

00:04:27.000 --> 00:04:30.380
Well, so anyway, I'm like, crazy popular.

00:04:30.380 --> 00:04:32.750
That makes it sound like you have no problems at all.

00:04:32.750 --> 00:04:36.540
But honestly, that's been kind of a hassle lately.

00:04:36.540 --> 00:04:39.830
Like, it's a drag having to deal with those guys.

00:04:42.040 --> 00:04:43.880
Sorry, you wouldn't get it.

00:04:45.290 --> 00:04:47.000
I kind of get it.

00:04:47.330 --> 00:04:52.670
I get annoyed at people who think
romance is the essence of life.

00:04:56.040 --> 00:04:57.460
Yeah, right?

00:04:57.920 --> 00:05:00.080
I guess that's why you're Nazuna's...

00:05:02.500 --> 00:05:05.540
